snippet: The Israeli military arrested four fishermen early Tuesday in what Palestinian officials said was a violation of the cease-fire agreement signed last month.
abstract: Israeli military arrests four Palestinian fishermen off the Gaza coast, suggesting that some disagreements remain over the details of the cease-fire agreement.
